game.name: Cartoon Racing Car Differences
game.description:
Do you think that you are sharp enough to recognize the differences in two images? Are you a type of individual who loves to be engaged in trick and engaging puzzles? If yes, you have reached at the right place since we have today brought to you a brand new arcade challenge where only putting your brainpower to the test can guide you towards the win. Try to be very quick as this is a time-based game! Lots of challenges and fun are waiting for you!

Your objective in this cute html5 puzzle game is to find out the small differences behind these two pictures. The best part is that this educational game will not only help to improve your concentration abilities but will also work well on enhancing your observation abilities. There are 10 levels and 7 differences to find out in each level in this wonderful racing car game. Make sure to get the job done fast before the time expires otherwise you would lose the game.

You would have one minute to spot all 7 differences and complete the game. It will be really exciting and amazing to find out them in a limited time and move to the advanced level. Play this cool fun cartoon difference game alone or with your friends and have fun to the fullest! We are damn sure that you would not get bored.
